## Open Questions

> [!IMPORTANT]
> **Auto-retry scope:** Should the autonomous retry loop apply to ALL diagnostic fixes (including the OpenAI-suggested ones), or only the deterministic regex-based rules (Tier-1)? OpenAI suggestions are probabilistic and could theoretically make things worse.

> [!IMPORTANT]
> **Retry limit:** Is 2 auto-retries (3 total attempts) acceptable, or do you want a different cap?

